name: Yupanquiando
description:
This token is a way to honor all singing souls, especially the beloved Atahualpa Yupanqui, a great Argentine singer.
Connected with the land, with the guitar, with silence and with the mountain, Don Atahualpa has left us an endless legacy of songs that have as much cultural value in Argentina as in many countries around the world. 
Thank you guitar, thank you Atahualpa.
